external_knowledge:
Recent investors: Joined the platform in the last three years;
Tech stocks: Stocks that belong to the 'Technology' sector;
Apple: Stock with the symbol 'AAPL';
Typical earnings surprise: Average surprise percentage for the sector.

- "beacons of the financial market" refers to stocks;
- "storm clouds" metaphorically represents alerts;
- "the most storm clouds" indicates the highest number of alerts;
- "top 3" means limiting the results to the first three;
- "gathering storm clouds" can be understood as accumulating alerts;

- "navigators" refers to the users, and "positions on the ship of finance" metaphorically refers to their roles.
- "signals of golden harvest" metaphorically refer to earnings-related alerts;
- "sea of stocks" metaphorically refers to the stock market.

sql:
SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM earnings e
WHERE e.surprise_percentage > (SELECT AVG(surprise_percentage) FROM earnings);

SELECT stock_symbol
FROM stocks
WHERE stock_id < 5;

SELECT dashboard_name
FROM dashboards
WHERE created_at > '2023-01-01 00:00:00';
